OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain, this locally heavy at first.
OL,7,FThe rain clearing by the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith a limited amount of brightness
OL,9,Femerging. However, a few showers may
OL,10,Fthen also develop.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FAny showers fading during the
OL,13,Fevening and most places becoming dry
OL,14,Fwith some clear spells here and there.
OL,15,FLight winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CMonday:FDry for many on bank holiday
OL,18,FMonday with bright or sunny spells
OL,19,Fdeveloping, particularly during the
OL,20,Fafternoon. Temperatures close to
OL,21,Fnormal for early May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
